<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Motivation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=35" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://education.calumet.purdue.edu/vockell/EdPsyBook/Edpsy5/Edpsy5_intrinsic.htm" class="external text" title="http://education.calumet.purdue.edu/vockell/EdPsyBook/Edpsy5/Edpsy5_intrinsic.htm" rel="nofollow">Factors of intrinsic motivation</a>: Brief introduction to intrinsic movitation and factors that influence intrinsic motivation.</li>
